          <div class="contentBlock">
            <h1 class="lowercaseHeading">What is this? </h1>
            <p class="textEnlarged">The Membership and Finance Report is presented to the <a href="index.html">Governing Body</a> each year. </p>
            <p class="lowercaseHeading"><span class="textEmphasis">It is a statistical overview of the key factors in the Church in Wales.</span> </p>
            <p class="lowercaseHeading">There are three main sections:</p>
            <ol>
              <li><a href="#memb">Membership</a></li>
              <li><a href="#finance">Finances</a></li>
              <li><a href="#prov">The Provincial Picture</a>  </li>
            </ol>
          </div>
          <div class="contentBlock">
            <h1>download</h1>
            <p>Download the Membership and Finance Report:</p>
