          <div class="contentBlock">
            <h1>membership and finance report </h1>
              <h2>Introduction</h2>
              <p class="introText">Each year parishes complete a standard questionnaire to provide information on key trends in attendance, income and expenditure across the Church inWales. The proportion of parishes responding to this annual survey is extremely high – 98.3% this year – and as a result it is possible for the Church to rely on this data for its planning both at a provincial and diocesan level. This report is intended to be a summary of the provincial picture; significantly more detailed reports are produced for diocesan use.</p>
